{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01BoceKhw4EJDGMKPbt5sFxY","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Summary\n\nHere's the complete information about the referral.ts file:\n\n### 1. Exported Factory Function\n\n**Name & Signature:**\n```typescript\nexport function createReferralRoutes(deps: ReferralRoutesDeps)\n```\n\n### 2. Dependencies Interface\n\n```typescript\nexport interface ReferralRoutesDeps {\n  db: Db;\n  sql: postgres.Sql;\n  config: Config;\n}\n```\n\n### 3. What It Exports\n\nThe function returns a **Hono app instance** with the following routes:\n\n- **POST /code** — Set or replace the player's referral code (validates code format, checks for duplicates)\n- **POST /apply** — Link an authenticated player to a referrer via their code (validates code exists, prevents self-referral, checks one-link-per-player)\n- **GET /code** — Retrieve the authenticated player's current referral code\n- **GET /stats** — Get referral summary stats (referred count, active count, volumes, earnings, pending balance)\n- **GET /earnings** — Paginated per-game earnings log (supports `page` and `limit` query params)\n- **POST /claim** — Request payout of pending referral earnings (async via queue event)\n- **GET /claim/:claimId** — Poll claim status (with transaction signature when complete)\n\nAll routes require wallet authentication (via `c.get(\"wallet\")`). The factory function also defines:\n\n- **CODE_REGEX**: `/^[a-z0-9-]{3,16}$/` — validates referral codes (3-16 lowercase alphanumeric + hyphens)\n- **REFERRAL_BASE_URL**: `https://taunt.bet/r` — base for shareable referral links\n\n---\n\n## Full File Content\n\nThe complete file is shown above (lines 1–449). Key patterns:\n- Error handling with structured error responses (error codes, messages, retryable flags)\n- Race condition handling for concurrent code/link claims (unique constraint checks)\n- Queue event emission for asynchronous claims (`emitEvent` + `EventTypes.REFERRAL_CLAIM_REQUESTED`)\n- Pagination support in earnings endpoint\n- Balance snapshots before claim insertion"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: aa47ad383eab2c697 (use SendMessage with to: 'aa47ad383eab2c697' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 41185\ntool_uses: 1\nduration_ms: 8933</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"193b62af-6140-4f02-b928-a21cc0840192","uuid":"087d9d02-15c1-439f-85f7-ed0f51666447","timestamp":"2026-03-25T12:15:18.756Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read the full content of `sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/routes/referral.ts` and show me:\n1. The exported factory function name and its signature\n2. The dependencies interface (ReferralRoutesDeps)\n3. What it exports\n\nReturn the full file content.","agentId":"aa47ad383eab2c697","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Summary\n\nHere's the complete information about the referral.ts file:\n\n### 1. Exported Factory Function\n\n**Name & Signature:**\n```typescript\nexport function createReferralRoutes(deps: ReferralRoutesDeps)\n```\n\n### 2. Dependencies Interface\n\n```typescript\nexport interface ReferralRoutesDeps {\n  db: Db;\n  sql: postgres.Sql;\n  config: Config;\n}\n```\n\n### 3. What It Exports\n\nThe function returns a **Hono app instance** with the following routes:\n\n- **POST /code** — Set or replace the player's referral code (validates code format, checks for duplicates)\n- **POST /apply** — Link an authenticated player to a referrer via their code (validates code exists, prevents self-referral, checks one-link-per-player)\n- **GET /code** — Retrieve the authenticated player's current referral code\n- **GET /stats** — Get referral summary stats (referred count, active count, volumes, earnings, pending balance)\n- **GET /earnings** — Paginated per-game earnings log (supports `page` and `limit` query params)\n- **POST /claim** — Request payout of pending referral earnings (async via queue event)\n- **GET /claim/:claimId** — Poll claim status (with transaction signature when complete)\n\nAll routes require wallet authentication (via `c.get(\"wallet\")`). The factory function also defines:\n\n- **CODE_REGEX**: `/^[a-z0-9-]{3,16}$/` — validates referral codes (3-16 lowercase alphanumeric + hyphens)\n- **REFERRAL_BASE_URL**: `https://taunt.bet/r` — base for shareable referral links\n\n---\n\n## Full File Content\n\nThe complete file is shown above (lines 1–449). Key patterns:\n- Error handling with structured error responses (error codes, messages, retryable flags)\n- Race condition handling for concurrent code/link claims (unique constraint checks)\n- Queue event emission for asynchronous claims (`emitEvent` + `EventTypes.REFERRAL_CLAIM_REQUESTED`)\n- Pagination support in earnings endpoint\n- Balance snapshots before claim insertion"}],"totalDurationMs":8933,"totalTokens":41185,"totalToolUseCount":1,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":10640,"cache_read_input_tokens":30022,"output_tokens":518,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":10640},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
